GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_PunctuationTypography> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_PunctuationTypography> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#PunctuationTypography> ;
    narr:childCount "21"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "59bd5ed36ac352bb25334d8e26ac6e9f09b65516" ;
    narr:narration """This hub catalogs the typographic and punctuation conventions defining the project's prose architecture. The [em-dash](narr:StyleObs_EmDashRhetoric) has historically served as the primary rhetorical engine, functioning as a [pivot for clarification](narr:StyleObs_EmDashDefinition), a [consequence amplifier](narr:StyleObs_DashAsAmplifier), and a [rhetorical pause](narr:StyleObs_EmDash_1). However, a recent [prohibition on em-dashes](narr:StyleObs_NoEmDashPolicy) has emerged, framing the mark as an \"AI tell\" to be replaced by standard punctuation. 

Beyond the dash, the system relies on [bold typography](narr:StyleObs_BoldEmphasis) to provide [scannable structural beats](narr:StyleObs_BoldBeats), [anchor architectural principles](narr:StyleObs_BoldKeyPrinciple), and [signal substitutive shifts](narr:StyleObs_SMB_BoldEmphasis). Other devices include [arrow notation](narr:StyleObs_ArrowNotation) for process flows, [parenthetical glosses](narr:StyleObs_ParenthesisGloss) for term definition, [italicized contrastive stress](narr:StyleObs_ItalicsForEmphasis), and [fenced code-block diagrams](narr:StyleObs_CodeBlockArchDiagram) that treat architecture as a static, readable artifact. The collection reflects a transition from using typography as a stylistic signature to treating it as a controlled, scannable interface for decision-making.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_EmDashQuote> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_NoEmDashes> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_2> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_3> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_5> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_ArrowNotation> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_BoldBeats> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_BoldEmphasis> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_BoldKeyPrinciple> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_Checkmark_Validation> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_CodeBlockArchDiagram> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_DashAsAmplifier> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_EmDashDefinition> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_EmDashRhetoric> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_EmDash_1> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_ForgettingBottleneck_BoldEmphasis> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_ItalicsForEmphasis> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_NoEmDashPolicy> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_ParenthesisGloss> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_RichTierBoldDecisionMarker> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_SMB_BoldEmphasis> ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "Replace em-dashes with commas, periods, or colons. The em-dash has become an AI tell." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_NoEmDashPolicy> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "**selection decides richness only — visibility is guaranteed for every area by the index.**" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_RichTierBoldDecisionMarker> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "SMB **replaces** enterprise as the primary market focus" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_SMB_BoldEmphasis> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "The physics never changed. The substrate did" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_3> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "**The buyer is plural.**" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_ForgettingBottleneck_BoldEmphasis> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The explicit prohibition of em-dashes as an 'AI tell' directly challenges the long-standing use of the dash as a rhetorical signature." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_NoEmDashes> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_EmDashQuote> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Typographic emphasis is split between aesthetic rhetorical cadence and functional, scannable navigation." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_EmDashRhetoric> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_BoldBeats> ] ;
    narr:writer "google/gemini-3.1-flash-lite" .
